emuInput.TitMainTitle: Portrait of baby Cheryl Banks wearing calico dress and seated on ottoman, in Banks home, 1838 Centre Avenue, Hill District
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 5, 1946, pg. 13, reads: "Sitting Pretty! A cute little lady...Cheryl Banks, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Nathaniel Banks Jr., who live at 1838 Centre Avenue.  She is the granddaughter of Mrs. Inez Jackson of the same address. - Courier Photo by Harris."
